OL,3,CResidents in Somerset to face 7.5%
OL,4,Ccouncil tax hike due to #66m deficit
OL,6,FFor Somerset Council, this means that
OL,7,Fit must somehow fill an existing #66m
OL,8,Fdeficit in its budget for 2025-6,
OL,9,Fwhich it says is being caused in a
OL,10,Flarge part by the growing demand and
OL,11,Fcost of adult social care.
OL,13,FIt's led to the council asking for
OL,14,Fpermission to increase taxes even more
OL,15,Fthan the usual amount, and along with
OL,16,Ffive others around the UK, it has now
OL,17,Fbeen given permission to do so.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
