OL,3,CResidents in Somerset to face 7.5%
OL,4,Ccouncil tax hike due to #66m deficit
OL,6,FThe 7.5% increase means that someone
OL,7,Fliving in an average Band D home will
OL,8,Fsee their total council tax bill for
OL,9,Fthe year rise from #1,728 up to #1,857.
OL,11,FPeople who spoke to ITV West Country
OL,12,Fabout the changes had mixed reactions.
OL,13,FOne person asked how the council could
OL,14,F"justify the increase" when services
OL,15,Fare being reduced, while a business
OL,16,Fowner said it makes "it a bit hard at
OL,17,Fthe moment... for everybody".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
