OL,3,CResidents in Somerset to face 7.5%
OL,4,Ccouncil tax hike due to #66m deficit
OL,6,FBut one man reflected that "the
OL,7,Fcouncil needs it for adult service so
OL,8,FI guess we just have to take it on the
OL,9,Fchin".
OL,11,FThe leader of Somerset Council, Cllr
OL,12,FBill Revans, said it is not a decision
OL,13,Fthat has been taken lightly, adding
OL,14,Fthat "No-one wants to put up council
OL,15,Ftax and we do recognise that this is
OL,16,Fout of a broken model of local
OL,17,Fgovernment finance.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
