OL,3,CResidents in Somerset to face 7.5%
OL,4,Ccouncil tax hike due to #66m deficit
OL,6,F"I think that's now understood by
OL,7,Fgovernment but we don't have a
OL,8,Fsolution yet, and the sooner we do
OL,9,Fhave a solution, particularly around
OL,10,Fadult social care, the easier it will
OL,11,Fget for local government to deliver
OL,12,Fthe services that people rely on."
OL,14,FCllr Revans also reflected that while
OL,15,Fthis measure may be a difficult one,
OL,16,Fit will not solve the council's issues
OL,17,Fwith its budget.
