OL,3,CResidents in Somerset to face 7.5%
OL,4,Ccouncil tax hike due to #66m deficit
OL,6,FHe added: "We've got a #66m gap and
OL,7,Fthis will raise us an extra #9m so,
OL,8,Fevery little helps and this helps a
OL,9,Flittle."
OL,11,FIt is likely the council will still
OL,12,Fneed to borrow money, sell some assets
OL,13,Fand potentially even cut more services
OL,14,Fin order to balance its budget.
OL,16,FThe measure to increase council tax
OL,17,Fneeds to be voted on by the full
OL,18,Fcouncil but would come into effect
OL,19,Ffrom 1st April if approved.
