OL,6,FDeputy Prime Minister Angela Rayner,
OL,7,Fwho approved the decision to allow
OL,8,FSomerset Council to increase its tax,
OL,9,Fsaid challenges remain in the
OL,10,Fgovernment's bid "to fix the broken
OL,11,Fsystem we inherited".
OL,13,FShe stressed the need to strike a
OL,14,Fbalance between preventing councils
OL,15,Ffrom experiencing "further financial
OL,16,Fdistress" and the "interests of
OL,17,Ftaxpayers".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
