OL,3,CResidents in Somerset to face 7.5%
OL,4,Ccouncil tax hike due to #66m deficit
OL,6,FITV News reported earlier this week
OL,7,Fthat almost every single council in
OL,8,FEngland is planning on raising council
OL,9,Ftax by the maximum amount possible.
OL,11,FOther councils are also looking at
OL,12,Fother measures to reduce their
OL,13,Fdeficits. Bristol City Council is
OL,14,Flooking at the possibility of only
OL,15,Fcollecting non-recyclable rubbish once
OL,16,Fa month, which would make it the first
OL,17,Fcity in the UK to do so.
